Body: The contribution ticker is on the main page, and can be found here: https://ico.1worldonline.com/  Quote When is planned  the launching  the technology of decentralization? Please see our roadmap, contained in the whitepaper, for this and other vital milestones. We already have a robust list of clients and partners, many of which are known Fortune 500 companies. Please check out live examples our some of the ads currently in rotation here: https://ico.1worldonline.com/examples  Quote from: oficman on October 24, 2017, 02:36:07 PM Quote from: susankhardman on October 24, 2017, 01:53:41 PM Quote from: Moore787 on October 22, 2017, 12:43:11 PM Would be the wallet for PC users are available? Quote Will the platform work in the future on mobile devices, i mean Android ?  We already have an app on the Google Play Store, please check us out! https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.oneworld.poller&hl=en   Quote Do you think you are competing with a YouTube or a Twitch?  This is not our aim. We do not host video or facilitate live streaming, as these two platforms do.   Quote I wonder where your currency will be possible to store?  Our token is compatible with any wallet that would accept and send ERC20 tokens! We suggest MEW; it is easy to use, fully featured and best of all, free!   Quote The technology blockchain and will be implemented after the ICO, to remove the bureaucracy. This will reduce the cost of providing services  This is correct. By building our token on the Ethereum blockchain, we are utilizing the security, trust and stability of said network.
